Wednesday, February 7, 2001

MERIT DOCKET

00-2153. State ex rel. Bair v. Fifth Dist. Court of Appeals.

In Mandamus. On complaint in mandamus by Jonathan D. Bair. On S.Ct.Prac.R. X(5) determination, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
